{"tid":1184502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特朗普訪英】工黨黨魁郝爾賓拒出席國宴 特朗普：倘對方任英國首相未必分享情報","createTime":"2019-06-03T15:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T17:59:11.000Z","uid":70063,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4a90cd8cd2d5294ac8e0476a12035d6e30ecac","tid":1184502,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普訪問英國，工黨領袖郝爾賓決定不出席英國政府款待他的國宴，特朗普回應稱沒有感到被冒犯，但認為郝爾賓未能夠與美國建立友誼將是一個錯誤，更揚言假如郝爾賓成為英國首相，他需要考慮是否繼續與英國分享最機密的情報。<br />\n<br />\n屬左翼陣營的郝爾賓，反特朗普已不是秘密，曾多次公開批評特朗普鼓吹的美國優先以及反移民等極右主張，又認為特朗普在脫歐問題上，有干預英國內政之嫌。事實上，特朗普亦早已表態，支持由保守黨的硬脫歐派、前倫敦市長約翰遜接任英國首相。<br />\n<br />\n至於同屬工黨的現任倫敦市長簡世德，同樣不滿意特朗普國事訪問英國，他批評特朗普對全球構成威脅，英國以紅地毯盛大歡迎他是有違英國作風(un-British)的表現，將來回望，也會是站於歷史錯誤的一方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190603/59670107?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR1seKzaUX1sNszD7iwyXZHBnvXunDUNw5vb8Fqkwmin5trVR9u6mtZAS8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59670107%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR1seKzaUX1sNszD7iwyXZHBnvXunDUNw5vb8Fqkwmin5trVR9u6mtZAS8g&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok4429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=07273d9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59670107%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR1seKzaUX1sNszD7iwyXZHBnvXunDUNw5vb8Fqkwmin5trVR9u6mtZAS8g&h=d7215b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190603/59670107?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR1seKzaUX1sNszD7iwyXZHBnvXunDUNw5vb8Fqkwmin5trVR9u6mtZAS8g</a>"},{"pid":"03df4fa4090184b321e7dca2ec5707953698b04a","tid":1184502,"uid":99962,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"一隻白左一隻回左叫囂，見證大英帝國沒落"},{"pid":"82338a06eca95eed4035fc97f6d53ebc549c5121","tid":1184502,"uid":142499,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"776363c3d7d7edd2cb49b726ab7c8f55de1dfb9c","tid":1184502,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"uk is going down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5319c764b4b98be5056b911ebb59eca0f07b3cbd","tid":1184502,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"繼續奶共囉"},{"pid":"21dee73f098748146822a237ab6209a63a798772","tid":1184502,"uid":127988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"03df4fa4090184b321e7dca2ec5707953698b04a","tid":1184502,"uid":99962,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"一隻白左一隻回左叫囂，見證大英帝國沒落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T17:59:11.000Z","msg":"咁張伯倫應該向希特拉投降啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}